<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About - Blog Platform</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Work+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f4f6fb;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --line: #dbe2ef;
        --text: #0f1830;
        --muted: #5f7392;
        --brand: #232d91;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { margin: 0; font-family: "Work Sans", sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }

      .platform-header { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .platform-header-inner { max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 12px 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; }
      .platform-brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; }
      .platform-brand svg { color: var(--brand); }
      .platform-nav { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
      .platform-nav a { color: #283d61; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px; }
      .platform-nav-active { color: var(--brand) !important; font-weight: 700 !important; }

      .topbar { background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .topbar-inner { max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 14px 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
      .brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; }
      .brand .logo { color: var(--brand); display: inline-flex; }
      .nav, .admin-nav { margin-left: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 22px; }
      .nav a, .admin-nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #283d61; font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px; }
      .nav a.active, .admin-nav a.active { color: var(--brand); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand); padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; }
      .menu { position: relative; }
      .menu-btn { border: 0; background: transparent; color: #283d61; font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px; cursor: pointer; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
      .menu-list { display: none; position: absolute; right: 0; top: 26px; width: 170px; background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(16,24,40,.12); padding: 6px 0; z-index: 40; }
      .menu-list.open { display: block; }
      .menu-list a, .menu-list button { display: block; width: 100%; border: 0; background: transparent; text-align: left; padding: 9px 12px; color: #2d4366; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; }
      .menu-list a:hover, .menu-list button:hover { background: #f3f6fd; color: var(--brand); }
      .avatar { width: 34px; height: 34px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--brand); color: #fff; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }

      .container { max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 26px 18px 0; }
      .hero { text-align: center; padding: 28px 0 34px; }
      .hero h1 { margin: 0 auto; max-width: 720px; font-size: 54px; line-height: 1.05; font-weight: 800; }
      .hero p { margin: 18px auto 0; max-width: 680px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; }

      .hero-image {
        margin-top: 18px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 420px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid #d8dfec;
        background:
          linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18,24,40,.08), rgba(18,24,40,.08)),
          url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366754035-f200968a6e72?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(16,24,40,.08);
      }

      .story-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr; gap: 24px; margin: 34px 0; }
      .story h2 { margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--brand); }
      .story p { margin: 0 0 14px; color: #334a6e; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.85; }
      .mission {
        background: #f7f9fe;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 22px;
      }
      .mission h3 { margin: 0 0 12px; color: var(--brand); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; }
      .mission blockquote { margin: 0; color: #243c62; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 16px; }

      .values-wrap {
        margin: 24px -18px 0;
        padding: 42px 18px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
        border-top: 1px solid #e7ecf5;
      }
      .values-head { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
      .values-head h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 800; }
      .values-head p { margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted); }
      .values-grid { max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 16px; }
      .value-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px; }
      .value-card .material-symbols-outlined { color: var(--brand); margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .value-card h4 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; }
      .value-card p { margin: 0; color: #5f7392; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }

      .cta {
        margin: 0 -18px;
        background: var(--brand);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 44px 18px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .cta h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 38px; font-weight: 800; }
      .cta .pill { margin: 12px auto 20px; display: inline-block; padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.14); color: #e2e8ff; font-size: 13px; }
      .cta-actions { display: inline-flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }

      .footer { background: #fff; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 28px 18px 16px; }
      .footer-inner { max-width: 1340px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #edf1f8; }
      .f-brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
      .f-brand svg { color: var(--brand); }
      .footer h5 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
      .footer p, .footer a { color: #6b7f9e; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: none; line-height: 1.7; }
      .copy { text-align: center; color: #8da0bb; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 12px; }

      @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .hero h1 { font-size: 42px; }
        .story-grid, .values-grid, .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .hero-image { height: 320px; }
      }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; }
        .cta h3 { font-size: 28px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% if (currentUser && currentUser.role === "admin") { %>
      <%- include("partials/admin-header", { activeAdminPage: "" }) %>
    <% } else if (currentUser) { %>
      <%- include("partials/auth-header", { activePage: "", navClass: "nav", showSearch: false }) %>
    <% } else { %>
      <%- include("partials/public-header", { activePage: "" }) %>
    <% } %>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Empowering the next generation of digital storytellers.</h1>
        <p>
          We are building the tools that professional publishers need to reach their audience,
          streamline their workflows, and grow their impact in a noisy digital world.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="hero-image" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <section class="story-grid">
        <div class="story">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>
            Founded with a vision to streamline editorial workflows, our platform was built to solve the
            friction points faced by professional publishers. We realized that while the web had evolved,
            the tools for managing high-volume editorial content had remained stagnant.
          </p>
          <p>
            What started as a small internal tool for a boutique agency quickly grew into a comprehensive
            platform used by thousands of creators worldwide. We believe in the power of words and the
            technology that carries them.
          </p>
        </div>
        <aside class="mission">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <blockquote>
            "To democratize professional-grade publishing tools, enabling every storyteller to build,
            manage, and scale their digital legacy without technical barriers."
          </blockquote>
        </aside>
      </section>
    </main>

    <section class="values-wrap">
      <div class="values-head">
        <h2>Core Values</h2>
        <p>The principles that guide every decision we make.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <article class="value-card">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">visibility</span>
          <h4>Transparency</h4>
          <p>We believe in open communication with users and within our team. No hidden agendas.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">lightbulb</span>
          <h4>Innovation</h4>
          <p>We constantly push boundaries of what is possible in digital content management.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
          <h4>User-Centricity</h4>
          <p>Our roadmap is built on user feedback. We exist to solve your publishing challenges.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="value-card">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_up</span>
          <h4>Scalability</h4>
          <p>Whether you are a solo blogger or a global newsroom, our tech grows with you.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <h3>Ready to transform your editorial workflow?</h3>
      <div class="pill">Join 50,000+ storytellers already using Blog Platform.</div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-grid">
          <div>
            <a class="f-brand" href="/">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 4h8v8H4zM12 12h8v8h-8zM4 14h6v6H4zM14 4h6v6h-6z"/></svg>
              <span>Blog Platform</span>
            </a>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;">Empowering digital storytellers everywhere.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5>Company</h5>
            <a href="/about">About</a><br />
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5>Legal</h5>
            <a href="/about">Privacy</a><br />
            <a href="/about">Terms</a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5>Social</h5>
            <a href="#">Share</a><br />
            <a href="#">RSS</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="copy">© 2026 Blog Platform Inc. All rights reserved.</div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <% if (currentUser) { %><script src="/js/auth-header.js"></script><% } %>
  </body>
</html>
